ance\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 278}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 340}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that is why Bardin, who performs as the drag queen Paloma, felt it was meaningful and important to be part ofa Paris Olympics opening ceremonythat presented a multifaceted, multiethnic France with people of different ethnicities and orientations.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6116782872148166e-15, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996749000972693, \"rank\": 0.00017100760097680696, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bardin\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"ceremonythat\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"different ethnicities\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"orientations\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a really important moment for the French people and the representation of France around the world,\\\" says Paloma, who took part in a single scene that has drawn some furious criticism - i