"part\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 737}, {\"ngram\": \"a single scene\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"some furious criticism\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"a disgrace\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the ceremony'sartistic director, Thomas Jolly, and other participants have repeatedly said the scene wasn't inspired by \\\"The Last Supper,\\\"critics interpreted that part of the showas a mockery of Leonardo Da Vinci's painting showing Jesus Christ and his apostles.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.8919864281700406, \"rank\": 0.1210095535000207, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.331241364861842e-19, \"text\": \"Leonardo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6273340121221507e-31, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999622455114, \"rank\": 3.7754437520358e-08, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony'sartistic director\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"other participants\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"the scene\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"The Last Supper,\\\"critics\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"that part\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"the showas\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"a mockery\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"his apostles\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma, best known for winning \\\"Drag Race France,\\\" appeared with other drag artists and dancers alongside Barbara Butch, a popular DJ who wore a silver headdress that looked like a halo.\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1171, \"end\": 1177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6116782872148166e-15, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 1277, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"score\": 0.9999897744159937, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Barbara Butch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barbara_Butch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Drag Race France\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"other drag artists\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"a popular DJ\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver headdress\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"a halo\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Butch has nowfiled a complaint alleging online abuse and harassment,and Paris police have launched an investigation.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8932916101863302e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Butch\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"harassment\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1425}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma is not, at this point, planning to take legal action over online harassment, and would prefer to focus on the many \\\"loving messages\\\" that have been pouring in.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6116782872148166e-15, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"legal action\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"the many \\\"loving messages\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The performer been getting thousands of messages daily, she told The Associated Press, most of them positive but some that he described as \\\"violent\\\" and even \\\"from the Middle Ages.\\\"\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999819050285692, \"rank\": 1.809529863761847e-05, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The performer\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"messages\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Middle Ages\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, there are no misgivings, despite the backlash.\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no misgivings\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma said she was proud to have been part of a show that did not rely on a series of French cliches - for example, \\\"the Parisian with a baguette under their arm.\\\"\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1880, \"end\": 1886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6116782872148166e-15, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 1967, \"end\": 1973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9810019444587764, \"rank\": 0.019361714537919784, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"a show\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"a baguette\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"their arm\", \"from\": 2033, \"to\": 2042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It could have been a postcard from 1930,\\\" she said of the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a postcard\", \"from\": 2066, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But instead, it was a photograph of France in 2024.\\\"\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2152, \"end\": 2158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996749000972693, \"rank\": 0.00017100760097680696, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photograph\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many agreed, and praised the ceremony for its creativity, style and showmanship.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"its creativity\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"style\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2233}, {\"ngram\": \"showmanship\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But French Catholic bishops and others were among those who said Christians had been offended, thoughParis Olympics organizers have saidthere was \\\"never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group\\\" but rather to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2256, \"end\": 2262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9810019444587764, \"rank\": 0.019361714537919784, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2263, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999513020169, \"rank\": 4.816738815880388e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http:/