gram\": \"our job\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The criticism, she said, has been fueled by hate.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The criticism\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"hate\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Where is the Catholicism, the Christianity in that?\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2956, \"end\": 2968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999986524890103, \"rank\": 1.3408812327286015e-06, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Catholicism\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is very hypocritical that their message is not about religion or kindness, it's about hate towards Jews, fat people, queer people and trans people.\\\"\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.993875448559567, \"rank\": 0.006160103861725826, \"text\": \"Jews\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their message\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"kindness\", \"from\": 3046, \"to\": 3054}, {\"ngram\": \"hate\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"fat people\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"trans\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3121, \"to\": 3127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been accused of trying to impose our vision on the world,\\\" Bardin said.\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngr