 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"her drag performance\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bardin debuted the drag queen persona some five years ago, the Spanish name inspired by the films of Pedro Almod\\u00f3var.\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3510, \"end\": 3517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9993605529515829, \"rank\": 0.0005129059895086275, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3548, \"end\": 3563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Almod\\u00f3var\", \"score\": 0.9999999575011325, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pedro Almod\\u00f3var\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Almod\\u00f3var\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pedro_Almod\\u00f3var\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bardin\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3453}, {\"ngram\": \"the drag queen\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3476}, {\"ngram\": \"the films\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if she had any regrets, Paloma replied: \\\"My only regrets is people's reactions.\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3596, \"end\": 3602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6116782872148166e-15, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any regrets\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3594}, {\"ngram\": \"My only regrets\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"people's reactions\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sorry if people are offended but we did not try to parody, to mock 'The Last Supper.'\", \"from\": 365